    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Persons who write original plays, such as tragedies, comedies, or dramas, or adapt themes from fictional, historical, or narrative sources, for dramatic presentation.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
